<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>This type defines a shape based on the same 3D mesh file format used by <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick3d-model.xml#source-prop">QtQuick3D.Model</db:link>.</db:para>
<db:para>Objects that are controlled by the physics simulation cannot use <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick3d-physics-trianglemeshshape.xml">TriangleMeshShape</db:link>: It can only be used with <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick3d-physics-staticrigidbody.xml">StaticRigidBody</db:link> and <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick3d-physics-dynamicrigidbody.xml#isKinematic-prop">kinematic bodies</db:link>. Use <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick3d-physics-convexmeshshape.xml">ConvexMeshShape</db:link> for non-kinematic dynamic bodies.</db:para>
