</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="property-documentation">
<db:title>Property Documentation</db:title>
<db:section xml:id="source-prop">
<db:title>source : url</db:title>
<db:fieldsynopsis>
<db:type>url</db:type>
<db:varname>source</db:varname>
<db:modifier>writable</db:modifier>
<db:synopsisinfo role="access">public</db:synopsisinfo>
<db:synopsisinfo role="status">active</db:synopsisinfo>
<db:synopsisinfo role="threadsafeness">unspecified</db:synopsisinfo>
</db:fieldsynopsis>
<db:para>This property defines the location of the mesh file used to define the shape.</db:para>
<db:para>Internally, <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick3d-physics-trianglemeshshape.xml">TriangleMeshShape</db:link> converts the mesh to an optimized data structure. This conversion can be done in advance. See the <db:link xlink:href="qtquick3dphysics-cooking.xml">cooking overview documentation</db:link> for details.</db:para>
</db:section>
